8/14(Sat.)Taiwan's health care ranked No. 1 in world for 2021/Taiwanese people's life expectancy rose to 81.3(Host:James)<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">There is no on-site meeting during the pandemic of COVID-19.<br /><br />加入 Zoom 會議<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... NKSU5MQT09<br /><br />會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br />At the presentation, the time limit is 1-2 minutes for each speaker.</span><br />-----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Taiwan's health care ranked No. 1 in world for 2021<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4106372">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4106372</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />Q1: Are you satisfied about the healthcare system in Taiwan, why?<br />Q2: Do you have the experience long stay in other countries? How about their healthcare system?<br />Q3: The vaccine coverage rate has increased in Taiwan recently, do you have vaccine injection already?<br />Q4: Some people went abroad to get vaccine injection, do you also plan to do it?<br />-------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Taiwanese people's life expectancy rose to 81.3<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.icrt.com.tw/info_details.php?mlevel1=6&amp;mlevel2=12&amp;news_id=207071">https://www.icrt.com.tw/info_details.ph ... _id=207071</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />Q1: Do you feel long life span is good for everyone?<br />Q2: Do you feel satisfy about your life? How do you improve it?<br />Q3: Do you retire? How do you make your life more interesting ?<br />Q4: Compare to lifespan, the birth rate in Taiwan is lowest in world, what’s the problem? How to improve it?<br />-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><span style="color: #0000FF">P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~</span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Tue Aug 10, 2021 12:54 am</p><hr />
